snippet.title: Bengaluru: IT Officials Seize Rs 5 crores in New Currency Notes from Engineer's House

localized.description:
Bengaluru: Income Tax officials seized Rs 5 crores in new currency notes from Engineer's house. Modi government is taking actions against those who are converting their black money into white and those who are helping them.
